data.description: Well maintained and updated home (#107) in Pomona Meadows 55+ community. New interior and exterior paint, new carpets, updated bathrooms, new furnace and heat pump, and new gutters all in 2021. Sunny front room, kitchen with lots of counter space, and breakfast nook with views of hills.  Primary bedroom has slider door that opens up to a new cedar deck and private back yard. Sprinkler system throughout the low maintenance landscaped property and a tool shed for storage.  There is a front driveway in addition to the deep carport covered driveway for plenty of off street parking.   Pomona Meadows is a great neighborhood close to everything The Dalles and Gorge has to offer. Come see this one today!
